FBIS4-65946 "drweu102_k_94002" FBIS-WEU-94-102 Daily Report 24 May 1994 PORTUGAL New Head of Secret Services Named New Head of Secret Services Named LD2505085694 Lisbon RDP Antena 1 Radio Network in Portuguese 1600 GMT 24 May 94 LD2505085694 Lisbon RDP Antena 1 Radio Network Portuguese BFN [Excerpt] Daniel Sanches is the new director general of the SIS [Portuguese Secret Services]. He was the director general of the border and immigration services and is thus replacing Ladeiro Monteiro, who resigned yesterday because of the services' irregular investigations in Madeira. He will be sworn in tomorrow at 1000. [passage omitted]
